reviewText: I have not bought this movie, but I have bought Saturday Matinee, (Dead Man's Gulch & Conquest of Cheyenne) and Saturday Matinee, ( Stagecoach to Denver & Homesteaders of Paradise Valley) and neither one of them will play correctly. I have tried them in my computer and my DVD Player and they just will play for a little bit and then quit. So be forewarned if this DVD is like the ones I got. Jay
